### 1. 创建标签接口测试
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "加班餐",
  "color": "#FF5733"
}

### 2. 创建标签接口测试 - 名称重复场景
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "加班餐",
  "color": "#33FF57"
}

### 3. 创建标签接口测试 - 使用默认颜色
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "交通",
  "color": null
}

### 4. 获取所有标签列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tags
Accept: application/json

### 5. 根据ID获取标签详情（替换{tagId}为实际ID）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tags/3
Accept: application/json

### 6. 更新标签信息（替换{tagId}为实际ID）
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/tags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 3,
  "name": "加班餐饮",
  "color": "#3357FF"
}

### 7. 更新标签接口测试 - 更新到已存在的名称（替换{tagId}为实际ID，{existingTagName}为另一个已存在的标签名）
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/tags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 3,
  "name": "交通",
  "color": "#FF33A8"
}

### 8. 更新标签接口测试 - 更新不存在的标签
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/tags
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 9999,
  "name": "不存在的标签",
  "color": "#000000"
}

### 9. 删除标签接口测试（替换{tagId}为实际ID）
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/tags/4
Accept: application/json

### 10. 删除不存在的标签
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/tags/9999
Accept: application/json

### 11. 获取不存在的标签
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tags/9999
Accept: application/json
